24:44.885 --> 24:46.985
♪ 'Cause we're riding ♪

24:49.223 --> 24:52.524
♪ It's just the streets
and you and me ♪

24:56.830 --> 24:59.164
♪ Heads up ♪

24:59.166 --> 25:01.533
♪ Don't look back ♪

25:06.240 --> 25:11.309
♪ On the streets of Tokyo,
no looking back ♪

