25:41.141 --> 25:42.474
Frankie?

25:42.476 --> 25:44.743
Hey.

25:44.745 --> 25:46.211
How'd you get in?

25:46.213 --> 25:47.646
You gonna hit me
with that?

25:50.884 --> 25:52.184
I made some coffee.

25:57.691 --> 26:00.793
I, uh, love what you've done
with the place.

26:02.830 --> 26:04.029
I had a party.

26:04.031 --> 26:05.363
Looks like
you had a few.

26:05.365 --> 26:07.365
Mm-hmm.
You get the money I sent?

26:07.367 --> 26:08.567
Yeah. Thanks.

26:10.771 --> 26:12.971
Kind of thought
I'd never see you again.

26:12.973 --> 26:14.840
Why would you think that?

26:14.842 --> 26:16.642
Because we
smoked crack together,

26:16.644 --> 26:18.777
and then,
you disappeared on me.

26:18.779 --> 26:21.980
I told you
I was coming back.

26:21.982 --> 26:25.116
I've got another job,
if you're interested.

26:25.118 --> 26:28.186
Yeah, well, I'm a...
I'm a little busy right now.

26:28.188 --> 26:29.455
Really?
Mm-hmm.

26:29.457 --> 26:33.525
Pulling jobs with Smurf
and your brothers?

26:33.527 --> 26:34.592
[ Scoffs ]

26:34.594 --> 26:37.529
You, uh...
hitting a bank?

26:37.531 --> 26:38.497
What?

26:41.001 --> 26:43.001
This is the main entrance.
That's the back.

26:43.003 --> 26:46.071
Drive through ATM. "PL" is,
uh, "parking lot," right?

26:46.073 --> 26:50.542
And I'm guessing the square
is a vault?

26:50.544 --> 26:51.943
A bank?

26:51.945 --> 26:53.611
There are cameras
everywhere.

26:53.613 --> 26:55.413
All the footage
uploads to the cloud.

26:55.415 --> 26:57.349
If you trip an alarm,
the cops'll be all over you.

26:57.351 --> 26:59.151
We've hit banks before.

26:59.153 --> 27:02.620
Smurf's gonna
get you killed.

27:02.622 --> 27:04.622
Believe it or not...

27:04.624 --> 27:06.325
we're actually
pretty good at this.

27:08.628 --> 27:11.363
I'll be in town
for a bit.

27:11.365 --> 27:14.700
There's a lot of money
on the table.

27:14.702 --> 27:17.369
If you don't end up in prison,
I'd love your help.

27:17.371 --> 27:19.104
Oh, yeah?

27:19.106 --> 27:22.274
Is that 'cause I'm, uh,
I'm good at what I do?

27:24.712 --> 27:27.779
Your, uh, friend's up.

27:27.781 --> 27:29.114
Maybe get her
a cup of coffee.

27:29.116 --> 27:32.151
♪♪

27:35.455 --> 27:38.424
♪♪

27:41.729 --> 27:43.595
Coffee?

27:43.597 --> 27:46.798
At 4:30,
I will take the Scout.

27:46.800 --> 27:49.335
I will buy gas
with your credit card

27:49.337 --> 27:51.803
at the Mobil on Vine...

27:51.805 --> 27:53.605
pump 4,
where the camera's out.

27:53.607 --> 27:55.006
Mm-hmm.

27:55.008 --> 28:00.078
Then, I will buy two tickets to
the new "Avengers" at the Regal.

28:00.080 --> 28:01.079
I'll sit through it,

28:01.081 --> 28:02.680
even though you know
I think that shit is lame.

28:02.682 --> 28:03.681
Yeah.

28:03.683 --> 28:06.484
And then,
I'll see you at home.

28:06.486 --> 28:09.087
[ Pops lips ]

28:09.089 --> 28:10.355
I can find
somebody else to do it

28:10.357 --> 28:12.157
if you're not
comfortable with it.

28:12.159 --> 28:14.426
No, I like being
your alibi.

28:25.239 --> 28:27.006
Craig's right,
you know?

28:30.310 --> 28:32.510
If you just
forget the cameras,

28:32.512 --> 28:35.113
and then...

28:35.115 --> 28:38.049
surf the way
you've always surfed...

28:38.051 --> 28:40.919
I know. And tons of guys
would kill to be on the circuit.

28:43.123 --> 28:47.125
I'm an asshole if I don't
give it a shot.

28:47.127 --> 28:54.933
Well, whatever you want to do,
I'm cool with it.

28:54.935 --> 28:58.303
♪♪

29:02.610 --> 29:04.342
You want
sushi tonight?

29:04.344 --> 29:08.147
♪♪

29:11.085 --> 29:15.087
♪♪

29:17.891 --> 29:23.295
Your brothers wanted me
to pull you off this job.

29:23.297 --> 29:25.096
They think you're
out of control, baby.

29:25.098 --> 29:26.432
Are you out
of control?

29:31.038 --> 29:33.171
- You ready?
- He's ready.

29:33.173 --> 29:36.809
♪♪

29:39.913 --> 29:43.415
♪♪

29:46.654 --> 29:48.253
[ Engine starts ]

29:51.725 --> 29:55.393
[ Motion's
"Pardon My Reflection" plays ]

29:55.395 --> 29:57.663
♪ Still I come out
half a man ♪

29:57.665 --> 30:00.132
♪ Not so much
the constant talking ♪

30:00.134 --> 30:01.599
♪ But the words
are hard to ground ♪

30:01.601 --> 30:03.735
Man: Then, it got weird. Somebody
had something in their boot.

30:03.737 --> 30:05.270
Well, it sounds like
she came through.

30:05.272 --> 30:06.271
Yeah.

30:06.273 --> 30:07.739
She was fine,
this time.

30:07.741 --> 30:09.207
Fine?

30:09.209 --> 30:10.476
If it wasn't for her,
you'd be bleeding out

30:10.478 --> 30:12.010
in the back of
a cop car.

30:12.012 --> 30:14.212
If you want your girlfriend
on the job, that's your choice.

30:14.214 --> 30:15.213
Get your own crew.

30:15.215 --> 30:16.414
What is
your problem?

30:16.416 --> 30:17.816
She makes us stick out.

30:17.818 --> 30:19.351
We're wearing masks.

30:19.353 --> 30:20.752
Nobody could tell
she's a girl...

30:20.754 --> 30:21.953
She's a hundred pounds soaking
wet,

30:21.955 --> 30:23.088
and her hair's going
down to her ass...

30:23.090 --> 30:24.422
Nobody saw her hair.

30:24.424 --> 30:25.891
She's a nice piece of tail.
Good for you.

30:25.893 --> 30:27.893
Good for you.
That doesn't make her one of us.

30:27.895 --> 30:29.961
What? What? What?

30:29.963 --> 30:31.029
Let's chill out.

30:31.031 --> 30:32.031
Get rid of her.

30:38.238 --> 30:41.773
Smurf: I got two cigarettes,
couple a sodas.

30:41.775 --> 30:42.708
Thanks, babe.

30:46.514 --> 30:50.382
♪ Now, I've stood here
long enough ♪

30:50.384 --> 30:51.950
♪ Knowing what I see ♪

31:05.132 --> 31:06.398
You know
what you want?

31:06.400 --> 31:07.933
Rosie.

31:07.935 --> 31:10.468
I like that.

31:10.470 --> 31:13.405
Uh, could I get you
something to drink?

31:13.407 --> 31:15.273
Yeah. Could I get
a coffee, please?

31:15.275 --> 31:16.241
Yeah.

31:20.480 --> 31:24.616
Her kid took a shit
on the carpet.

31:24.618 --> 31:29.355
Just dropped his pants
for no reason, right there.

31:29.357 --> 31:32.490
Didn't... didn't want to go
to preschool, or some shit.

31:32.492 --> 31:35.093
And she... she didn't even
notice for a day and a half,

31:35.095 --> 31:37.295
so the whole
apartment stinks.

31:37.297 --> 31:39.697
[ Scoffs ] And she wants me
to replace the carpet.

31:39.699 --> 31:41.633
I mean, do I have to do that,
legally, or is that...?

31:41.635 --> 31:43.769
No, no. You take it out of
her security deposit.

31:43.771 --> 31:45.703
She pays 200 bucks
a month.

31:45.705 --> 31:48.040
There is no
security deposit.

31:48.042 --> 31:49.174
And Smurf moved her there

31:49.176 --> 31:51.443
because her brother's in CHP
or some shit.

31:51.445 --> 31:52.844
Are we getting anything
from him?

31:52.846 --> 31:55.180
No. He retired
three years ago.

31:55.182 --> 31:57.315
I don't understand how they
didn't notice that there was,

31:57.317 --> 32:01.319
like, a pile of shit on the
carpet for a day and a half.

32:01.321 --> 32:02.921
That's what
I'm saying.

32:02.923 --> 32:04.923
I mean, how... how much does
a carpet even cost?

32:04.925 --> 32:08.293
Hey, Pope, what are you gonna do
with your buildings, man?

32:10.931 --> 32:13.398
Pope?

32:13.400 --> 32:15.801
What?

32:15.803 --> 32:18.804
I said "What are you gonna
do with your buildings?"

32:18.806 --> 32:20.205
The ones that
Smurf gave you.

32:24.344 --> 32:26.011
I don't know.

32:26.013 --> 32:29.547
Well, what do you think
you're gonna do?

32:29.549 --> 32:31.417
Why? You want them?

32:31.419 --> 32:33.084
What? No.

32:33.086 --> 32:34.686
I was just...

32:34.688 --> 32:38.624
I mean, you could sell them
or something.

32:38.626 --> 32:39.792
Yeah. Maybe.

32:42.496 --> 32:43.895
[ Door chimes ]

32:43.897 --> 32:52.638
♪♪

32:52.640 --> 32:54.973
J: Aw, shit.

32:54.975 --> 32:56.642
I am so sorry.

32:56.644 --> 32:57.643
